NEW YORK
GOVERNMENT OFFICES Closed.  POST OFFICES Express Mail only; the main post office on Eighth Avenue at 32nd Street is open for window service.  BANKS Most are closed.  PARKING Alternate-side parking rules are suspended. Parking meter regulations are in effect.  SANITATION Regular collections.  SCHOOLS Closed.  FINANCIAL MARKETS Stock and bond markets are closed.  TRANSPORTATION New York City subways and buses will operate on regular schedules. Long Island Rail Road and Metro-North trains will operate on holiday schedules.
NEW JERSEY
GOVERNMENT OFFICES Federal and state offices are closed.  POST OFFICES Express Mail only.  BANKS Most are closed.  SCHOOLS Most are closed.  TRANSPORTATION New Jersey Transit and PATH trains will operate on regular schedules.
CONNECTICUT
GOVERNMENT OFFICES Federal and state offices are closed.  POST OFFICES Express Mail only.  BANKS Most are closed.  SCHOOLS Most are closed.  TRANSPORTATION Metro-North trains will operate on holiday schedules.
